00:18:48,840 --> 00:18:51,170
Not bad. Let's prepare for the next scene.

290
00:18:57,960 --> 00:18:59,960
Angelica egg and brown sugar drink.

291
00:19:00,800 --> 00:19:02,480
Don't look at me. I didn't prepare it.

292
00:19:02,480 --> 00:19:03,940
Your husband prepared it.

293
00:19:04,600 --> 00:19:05,400
He's here?

294
00:19:05,920 --> 00:19:07,320
He arranged it remotely.

295
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:13,360
As if you deserve it.

296
00:19:13,360 --> 00:19:14,560
Keep standing there.

297
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:16,440
Cut!

298
00:19:17,440 --> 00:19:18,000
Okay.

299
00:19:24,480 --> 00:19:25,680
What scene are you acting out?

300
00:19:25,680 --> 00:19:27,200
It's your husband.

301
00:19:27,360 --> 00:19:29,320
He knows you have a water-splashing scene today.

302
00:19:29,320 --> 00:19:31,520
He specifically asked me to check on you.

303
00:19:31,520 --> 00:19:32,240
He's here.

304
00:19:34,160 --> 00:19:34,620
Come on.

305
00:19:35,160 --> 00:19:37,600
Smile! I need to take a photo to check in.

306
00:19:38,560 --> 00:19:39,820
I'll send it to him too.

307
00:19:43,200 --> 00:19:44,730
What do you need a knife for?

308
00:19:45,480 --> 00:19:46,740
I want to try my skills.

309
00:19:46,840 --> 00:19:49,080
Here's an extraordinary...

310
00:19:49,520 --> 00:19:49,960
Knife.

311
00:19:52,440 --> 00:19:54,770
I didn't know you had such amazing skills.

312
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:55,920
Well.

313
00:19:58,960 --> 00:20:00,360
The way you're flailing around

314
00:20:00,360 --> 00:20:01,800
makes it hard to focus.

315
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:05,130
I can't help it. I attract mosquitoes.

316
00:20:12,920 --> 00:20:13,680
Thank you.

317
00:20:13,960 --> 00:20:16,890
Our guest star, award-winning actress Ms. Ni Shang.

318
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:19,280
Shen Yifan sent it.

319
00:20:19,840 --> 00:20:21,500
Looks like it's meant for you.

320
00:20:23,600 --> 00:20:24,680
He sent it?

321
00:20:36,160 --> 00:20:37,400
Are you okay, Ms. Zheng?

322
00:20:37,400 --> 00:20:38,240
I'm fine.

323
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:42,530
Director, let's continue.

324
00:20:42,760 --> 00:20:43,220
Come on.

325
00:20:43,800 --> 00:20:44,960
Alright, ready.

326
00:20:45,800 --> 00:20:46,360
Action.

327
00:21:10,200 --> 00:21:10,840
Forget it.

328
00:21:11,640 --> 00:21:13,240
Better not make him worry.

329
00:21:16,600 --> 00:21:17,040
Shen.

330
00:21:26,720 --> 00:21:27,650
Why are you here?

331
00:21:32,920 --> 00:21:33,920
Give me your hand.

332
00:21:34,680 --> 00:21:35,400
No need, I can do it myself.

333
00:21:35,400 --> 00:21:36,930
Just listen to me this once.

334
00:21:43,520 --> 00:21:45,580
In your heart, he might seem perfect.

335
00:21:46,360 --> 00:21:47,360
But in my opinion,

336
00:21:47,560 --> 00:21:49,400
he's not a qualified boyfriend.

337
00:21:50,600 --> 00:21:51,240
He's not what you think.

338
00:21:51,240 --> 00:21:51,970
Listen to me.

339
00:21:52,560 --> 00:21:54,220
The old man wants me to go back.

340
00:21:54,400 --> 00:21:55,130
It's urgent.

341
00:21:55,760 --> 00:21:56,680
I might not be able

342
00:21:56,680 --> 00:21:58,040
to watch over you at the set every day.

343
00:21:58,040 --> 00:21:59,100
But remember this.

344
00:22:00,280 --> 00:22:01,480
Fame brings trouble.

345
00:22:02,400 --> 00:22:03,320
I worry about you,

346
00:22:03,320 --> 00:22:05,050
so I asked him to accompany you.

347
00:22:07,080 --> 00:22:08,410
Let me emphasize again.

348
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:11,000
This doesn't mean I'm giving up.

349
00:22:18,400 --> 00:22:20,120
Where is everyone?

350
00:22:22,440 --> 00:22:24,970
Which outfit should I wear for the next scene?

351
00:22:27,360 --> 00:22:28,520
Is it this one?

352
00:22:31,360 --> 00:22:32,600
Why are you here?

353
00:22:33,160 --> 00:22:34,160
You said

354
00:22:34,160 --> 00:22:36,360
you wanted a boyfriend delivered here.

355
00:22:41,480 --> 00:22:43,200
Is your hand still hurting?

356
00:22:43,720 --> 00:22:44,640
Not anymore.

357
00:22:47,640 --> 00:22:49,040
Who put this plaster on?

358
00:22:49,520 --> 00:22:51,380
I'll put a new one on for you later.

359
00:22:54,080 --> 00:22:55,320
What are you smiling at?

360
00:22:55,320 --> 00:22:56,680
You're jealous.

361
00:23:05,200 --> 00:23:05,880
Come here.

362
00:23:16,800 --> 00:23:17,760
Sir.

363
00:23:18,200 --> 00:23:19,000
At a time like this,

364
00:23:19,000 --> 00:23:21,040
shouldn't you show some restraint?

365
00:23:22,320 --> 00:23:23,160
I'm jealous

366
00:23:23,760 --> 00:23:24,760
and can't help it.

367
00:23:28,640 --> 00:23:30,570
I asked Wu Yu to send everyone away.

368
00:23:30,800 --> 00:23:33,000
They should all be having coffee by now.

369
00:23:47,880 --> 00:23:49,880
Why is your style different today?

370
00:23:49,920 --> 00:23:52,250
You've turned into a sighing Zheng Daiyu.

371
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:56,160
It feels like forever since I last saw him.

372
00:23:56,360 --> 00:23:57,960
I miss him so much.

373
00:23:59,600 --> 00:24:02,440
You just saw each other 10 minutes ago.

374
00:24:02,560 --> 00:24:04,320
We're filming right now.

375
00:24:04,320 --> 00:24:06,650
I'm the male lead standing in front of you.

376
00:24:09,480 --> 00:24:11,680
If only the male lead in this film with me

377
00:24:11,680 --> 00:24:13,040
could be him instead.

378
00:24:15,840 --> 00:24:18,080
You can use your imagination.

379
00:24:18,080 --> 00:24:20,160
Just pretend I'm him.

380
00:24:20,400 --> 00:24:22,600
This human prop doesn't mind at all.

381
00:24:24,880 --> 00:24:27,240
That's actually a good idea.

382
00:24:51,000 --> 00:24:51,560
General,

383
00:24:51,720 --> 00:24:53,640
you've done great service in repelling the enemy this time.

384
00:24:53,640 --> 00:24:55,560
The Emperor hinted that you should become a royal son-in-law.

385
00:24:55,560 --> 00:24:56,920
Why did you refuse?

386
00:24:56,920 --> 00:24:58,480
A man's ambition lies in the four corners of the world.

387
00:24:58,480 --> 00:24:59,880
Why bother with romance?

388
00:25:00,760 --> 00:25:01,800
Life is long.

389
00:25:02,320 --> 00:25:04,250
Should the rest of my bright future

390
00:25:04,560 --> 00:25:06,000
be tied to a woman's hand?

391
00:25:10,080 --> 00:25:10,840
Who?

392
00:25:19,600 --> 00:25:22,330
I fell in love with you at first sight when I was 16.

393
00:25:22,520 --> 00:25:25,080
You promised me I would be a general's wife.

394
00:25:25,080 --> 00:25:27,010
Now you're going back on your word.

395
00:25:31,520 --> 00:25:32,240
Who?

396
00:25:38,240 --> 00:25:39,080
Thanks.

397
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:43,040
Did I say you could leave?

398
00:25:45,680 --> 00:25:47,240
You really don't know how to treat a lady.

399
00:25:47,240 --> 00:25:48,840
Who was just claiming

400
00:25:49,400 --> 00:25:51,160
to be a general's wife?

401
00:25:51,440 --> 00:25:52,240
You...

402
00:25:53,200 --> 00:25:55,800
Never mind. I have urgent matters to attend to.

403
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:57,610
Thank you, General.

404
00:25:58,240 --> 00:25:59,370
Until we meet again.

405
00:26:04,560 --> 00:26:06,090
General, as you predicted,

406
00:26:06,160 --> 00:26:08,000
the wanted woman in red is nearby.

407
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:09,800
Also, the young master has arrived

408
00:26:09,800 --> 00:26:12,730
and met secretly with Lord Niu and Lord Ma last night.

409
00:26:17,760 --> 00:26:18,680
We received intelligence

410
00:26:18,680 --> 00:26:21,080
that the assassin who tried to kill Lord Ma is wounded

411
00:26:21,080 --> 00:26:22,680
and hiding in this teahouse.

412
00:26:22,760 --> 00:26:23,890
Search thoroughly.

413
00:26:24,040 --> 00:26:25,560
We'll find her for sure.

414
00:26:25,640 --> 00:26:26,360
Search!

415
00:26:28,680 --> 00:26:30,410
We can't just wait to be caught.

416
00:26:46,800 --> 00:26:47,330
Let's go.

417
00:26:49,800 --> 00:26:51,640
The lord says this person is the Red Robe Bandit.

418
00:26:51,640 --> 00:26:52,320
Arrest her!

419
00:27:00,840 --> 00:27:01,840
My people.

420
00:27:03,480 --> 00:27:04,810
How dare you touch them.

